answers.text: @michelleetann i don’t have specific recipe. But making this, you just need 1. mashed potato (boil or steam potato until soft), 2. mince meat (cook first with garlic or onion  with soya sauce) 3. Add cooked meat into mashed potato, season with salt n pepper. Let it cool 4. Make shape round or oval 5. Dip into 1 beaten egg and coated with breadcrumbs 5. Ready to fried
